        "body": [
            {
                "type": "section", 
                "id": "s0", 
                "title": "Main text", 
                "content": [
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "Wildenberg GA, Murray AW. 2014. Evolving a 24-hr oscillator in budding yeast. <i>eLife</i> <b>3</b>:e04875. doi: <a href=\"http://dx.doi.org/10.7554/eLife.04875\">10.7554/eLife.04875</a>. Published 10 November 2014"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "In the published article, Figure 4A listed 8 mutated genes incorrectly. In the text, we referred to the causative alleles of the mutated genes by their allele names (e.g., <i>sir4-100</i>), but in Figure 4A we mistakenly used the nature of the mutations (e.g., <i>sir4-L1012P</i>) as their allele names. This figure has been corrected to give both the allele names and the nature of each mutation."
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "Figures 4B, 4C and 4D are correct and unchanged from the original published figure, and we apologize for the original mistake."
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "The corrected Figure 4 is shown below:"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "image", 
                        "id": "fig1", 
                        "alt": "", 
                        "uri": "https://publishing-cdn.elifesciences.org/07532/elife-07532-fig1-v1.tif", 
                        "image": "elife-07532-fig1-v1.tif", 
                        "filename": "elife-07532-fig1-v1.tif"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "The originally published Figure 4 is also shown for reference:"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "image", 
                        "id": "fig2", 
                        "alt": "", 
                        "uri": "https://publishing-cdn.elifesciences.org/07532/elife-07532-fig2-v1.tif", 
                        "image": "elife-07532-fig2-v1.tif", 
                        "filename": "elife-07532-fig2-v1.tif"
                    }, 
                    {
                        "type": "paragraph", 
                        "text": "The article has been corrected accordingly."
                    }
                ]
            }
        ], 
